data.title: Black Crowes at Bulldog Bash
data.meta_description: Chris Robinson, lead singer of the Black Crowes, belts out a song Friday night during Bulldog Bash. The influential American blues-rock band headlined the event, which also featured the Battle of the Bands winner the Fides and country music performer Chris Young. Click here to see more photos from Friday's event.
